title: 165:  Free agency edition
itunes:title: 165:  Free agency edition
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks talk about the latest free agency news and how the signings will impact their new teams. DJ and Bucky also discuss Oklahoma running back Joe Mixon’s pro day and when he can expect to hear his name called during the NFL Draft.
